// Amazon S3 Glacier is a secure, durable, and extremely low-cost cloud storage service for data archiving and long-term backup.


// Key terms
* Archive -base unit of storage
* Vault - container for storing the archives
* Vault access policy


Ways of Retrieving
* Expedited - highest cost (1-5hours)
* Standard - (3-5hours)
* Bulk - least expensive (5-12hours)

// Has no upfront cost

// Using S3 Glacier
* REST API
* Java or .NET SDKs
* Amazon s3 lifecycles



